- Read files, encrypt content, save encrypted version. Implement decryption. Handle various file types.
Report Card Generator
- Read student marks from file, calculate grades, generate formatted report cards as text files.
Attendance with Biometric Simulation
- Simulate biometric attendance system. Store attendance with timestamps. Generate monthly reports, late coming analysis.
E-Wallet System
- Create digital wallet with add money, spend, transaction history. Store encrypted data in files.
Complaint Management System
- Register complaints, assign to departments, track status, resolution. Store all data with timestamps.
Certificate Generator
- Read participant names from file, generate certificates (text-based), save individually named files.
Auction System
- Create item listings, bid tracking, winner declaration. Store auction history, generate sale reports.
